The paper deals with generating adversarial examples for iris recognition systems, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning methods and auto-encoder networks, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the security implications of the attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with image processing techniques, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
